{
  "ComponentID": "DW01A",
  "ComponentType": "Single-Cell Lithium-Ion/Polymer Battery Protection IC",
  "Description": "The DW01A is a protection IC designed for single-cell lithium-ion or lithium-polymer battery packs. It monitors battery voltage and current to provide protection against overcharge, overdischarge, overcurrent (both charge and discharge), and short-circuit conditions. It achieves this by controlling external N-channel MOSFETs in series with the battery, features built-in protection delay timers, and supports charging from 0V.",
